{"tid":1623343,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「十八區勇武聯賽正式開始」","createTime":"2019-10-04T20:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:38:25.000Z","uid":76234,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4689ada77fe87b4b0d188440bb8c4dbd3302f67e","tid":1623343,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:04:36.000Z","msg":"為咗令各位手足不斷進步，<br />\n維持良性競爭可以幫助各位互相學習、進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n根據不同武力破壞程度而評分，<br />\n <br />\n由於我地「不會」主動傷人，只會自衛，<br />\n <br />\n故此神獸將不納入評分準則。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n每星期將選出最具破壞力區位，<br />\n <br />\n希望可作為其他17區參考之用，<br />\n <br />\n而最弱既幾區將會被手足恥笑，<br />\n <br />\n希望可用激將法將潛在勇武程度跟上大隊，<br />\n <br />\n各位，共勉。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n覺得有得諗再follow up<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017ff337e6cf2b97548c08f398e7dfd1893d4a16","tid":1623343,"uid":134141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:05:33.000Z","msg":"屯門一定係首三位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf2bca736937b7275c8baecabd1f3220451d506","tid":1623343,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:05:44.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得on9就由佢沉，<br />\n <br />\n我補多句Sorry，因為阻住大家睇post"},{"pid":"b26ba5109df9bec1d72b492d72e3cbb79d54a348","tid":1623343,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:06:12.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得on9就由佢沉，<br />\n <br />\n我補多句Sorry，因為阻住大家睇post"},{"pid":"1f5ab659715f0d783df0a3a3db6c7fc9ef7c577a","tid":1623343,"uid":76234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:06:55.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得on9就由佢沉，<br />\n <br />\n我補多句Sorry，因為阻住大家睇post"},{"pid":"14858c44b9707dac0765b17850566418a30c1c61","tid":1623343,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dis